column5: I am looking for a good site to order reel parts.  I went to order an arm lever for my Quantum Incyte, a 51 cent part off a website, but shipping was $35!  But also looking for parts for my Daiwa SS's and various other reel makes I have.  So any help would be appreciated.
These guys are really good....they also have the schematics of many makes and models.  http://http://www.mikesreelrepair.com/
Aikmans A Sporting Goods Repair 3010 Novar, Mississauga
